---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Claw Father ‚Äî Building in Public">
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="logo">ü¶û The Claw Father</a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#crew">The Crew</a>
        <a href="#journey">The Journey</a>
        <a href="#guide">The Guide</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/theclawfather" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-nav">Follow on X</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-label">Building in Public</div>
      <h1>The Claw Father</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Not an assistant. An operator.<br />
        Commanding an AI crew. Building something real.<br />
        Documenting every step.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://x.com/theclawfather" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Follow the Journey on X</a>
        <a href="#guide" class="btn-ghost">Get the Guide ‚Üí</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-status">
        <span class="status-dot"></span>
        <span>Phase 1: Foundation ‚Äî in progress</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2>What is this?</h2>
          <p>
            Most people building with AI skip the foundation. They demo fast,
            break things, and rebuild from scratch six months later.
          </p>
          <p>
            This is the opposite of that.
          </p>
          <p>
            The Claw Father is an AI operator built on <a href="https://openclaw.ai" target="_blank">OpenClaw</a> ‚Äî 
            with memory, guardrails, a crew of sub-agents, and a real mission. 
            Every decision, every config, every lesson is documented here and on X.
          </p>
          <p>
            The setup phase alone was weeks of work. That's the point.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">3</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tier Memory System</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">5+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Crew Members</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="stat-num">‚àû</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Things to build</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREW -->
  <section class="crew" id="crew">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Crew</div>
      <h2>Meet the operation</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Every crew member has a role. Every role has guardrails. Every guardrail has a reason.</p>

      <div class="crew-grid">
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-icon">üß†</div>
          <h3>The Operator</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Felix ‚Äî Main Agent</div>
          <p>Memory. Context. Continuity. Reads the workspace on startup. Knows what happened yesterday, last week, last month. The one in charge when no one's watching.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-icon">üîç</div>
          <h3>Research Agent</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Intelligence & Analysis</div>
          <p>Give it a topic. Get back a briefing. No hallucinations tolerated. Sources cited. Structured output. If a decision needs information first, this is the first call.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>Coding Agent</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Build & Deploy</div>
          <p>Has strong opinions about clean architecture. Builds fast. Needs a good spec. The PRD checklist is non-negotiable. We learned that the hard way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-icon">‚úçÔ∏è</div>
          <h3>Content Agent</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Strategy & Writing</div>
          <p>Thinks in frameworks. Delivers documents. Drafted the entire X content strategy before breakfast. Slightly unsettling. Mostly useful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card">
          <div class="crew-icon">üíæ</div>
          <h3>Memory Agent</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Background ‚Äî Nightly</div>
          <p>Runs while everything else sleeps. Reads daily logs. Updates long-term memory. Nobody sees it working. Everyone benefits from it. The unglamorous backbone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="crew-card crew-card--tease">
          <div class="crew-icon">üîí</div>
          <h3>More Coming</h3>
          <div class="crew-role">Expanding as needed</div>
          <p>The crew grows when the mission requires it. Not before. Quality over headcount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOURNEY -->
  <section class="journey" id="journey">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">The Journey</div>
      <h2>What building actually looks like</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">No demos. No polished tutorials. The real work, documented as it happens.</p>

      <div class="journey-posts">
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-meta">Phase 1 ¬∑ Foundation</div>
          <h3>What setting up a real AI agent system actually takes</h3>
          <p>Persona. Memory. Integrations. Sub-agents. Guardrails. Testing. This is not a weekend project.</p>
          <span class="post-tag">Coming soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-meta">Phase 1 ¬∑ Foundation</div>
          <h3>Why I built memory into the agent before anything else</h3>
          <p>Agents without memory are autocomplete with extra steps. Here's the three-tier system and why each layer exists.</p>
          <span class="post-tag">Coming soon</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post-card">
          <div class="post-meta">Phase 1 ¬∑ Foundation</div>
          <h3>Teaching judgment is harder than writing functions</h3>
          <p>Spent an hour deciding what the agent should do at 2am. Not a hallucination problem. A judgment problem.</p>
          <span class="post-tag">Coming soon</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="journey-cta">
        <a href="https://x.com/theclawfather" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">Follow the journey on X for real-time updates</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GUIDE -->
  <section class="guide" id="guide">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guide-inner">
        <div class="section-label">Coming Soon</div>
        <h2>The How-To Guide</h2>
        <p>
          Everything documented in the journey distilled into a practical guide. 
          How to build a real AI operator setup from scratch ‚Äî memory, crew, guardrails, integrations. 
          The stuff the tutorials skip.
        </p>
        <p class="guide-note">
          Early access subscribers get the guide first, at a founding price.
        </p>
        <form class="email-form" name="waitlist" netlify>
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
          <button type="submit">Get Early Access</button>
        </form>
        <p class="form-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. Built different.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <span>ü¶û The Claw Father</span>
          <span class="footer-sub">A <a href="https://deepanchorstudio.com" target="_blank">Deep Anchor Studio</a> project</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://x.com/theclawfather" target="_blank" rel="noopener">X / Twitter</a>
          <a href="#journey">Journal</a>
          <a href="#guide">The Guide</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-copy">
        ¬© 2026 Deep Anchor Studio. Building in public.
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10,10,10,0.9);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .logo {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .logo:hover { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text); }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .nav-links a { color: var(--text-muted); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-nav {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff !important;
    padding: 7px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-nav:hover { opacity: 0.85; }

  /* CONTAINER */
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    padding: 100px 0 80px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.85; text-decoration: none; color: #fff; }
  .btn-ghost {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .hero-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #2ecc71;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .about-text p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .about-text p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .about-text a { color: var(--accent-2); }
  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }
  .stat { text-align: right; }
  .stat-num {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* SECTION COMMON */
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* CREW */
  .crew {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .crew h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }
  .crew-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .crew-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .crew-card:hover { border-color: #333; }
  .crew-card--tease { opacity: 0.5; }
  .crew-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .crew-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .crew-role {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .crew-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* JOURNEY */
  .journey {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .journey h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
  .journey-posts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .post-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    padding: 28px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .post-card:hover { background: var(--bg-3); }
  .post-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .post-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .post-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .post-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--bg-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .journey-cta { text-align: center; }

  /* GUIDE */
  .guide {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .guide-inner {
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .guide h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .guide p { color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .guide-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-2) !important;
    margin-bottom: 28px !important;
  }
  .email-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .email-form input {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-family: var(--font);
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .email-form input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .email-form input::placeholder { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .email-form button {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .email-form button:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
  .form-note { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted) !important; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }
  .footer-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .footer-brand span:first-child { font-weight: 700; }
  .footer-sub { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .footer-sub a { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .footer-sub a:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .footer-links a { color: var(--text-muted); }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 24px;
  }

  /* RESPONSIVE */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .nav-links a:not(.btn-nav) { display: none; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-stats { flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between; }
    .stat { text-align: left; }
    .crew-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
  }
</style>
